        <Name>High-Efficiency Fertilizer</Name>
        <Note>Jerry's been busy studying new secret recipes. Test them for him. Go &lt;FONT COLOR="#009900"&gt;collect 3 Dung &lt;/FONT&gt;, and then &lt;FONT COLOR="#009900"&gt;use &lt;/FONT&gt;his &lt;FONT COLOR="#009900"&gt;special fertilizer &lt;/FONT&gt;to make &lt;FONT COLOR="#009900"&gt; High Efficiency Fertilizer.&lt;/FONT&gt; Then bring it to him.</Note>
        <Type>32</Type>
        <Description>1. Collect 3 &lt;FONT COLOR="#009999"&gt;Dung&lt;/FONT&gt;;&lt;BR&gt;2. Use item &lt;FONT COLOR="#009999"&gt;Special Test Potion&lt;/FONT&gt; to make &lt;FONT COLOR="#009999"&gt;High Efficiency Fertilizer&lt;/FONT&gt;.</Description>
